This paper involves computer vision and deep learning techniques to generate dental crowns, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of generative models and statistical compatibility also suggests that this paper could belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The incorporation of spatial profiles and space constraints may also suggest that this paper could belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and computational engineering (cs.CE) sub-categories.
